    "comments": [
        {
            "author": "Serukis",
            "comment": "Tasty tasty waffles. <3",
            "response": "Delicious accidents are the best accidents <3"
        },
        {
            "author": "Valcin",
            "comment": "Cool your mail and a tasty treat what an interesting idea waffle Phoenix so cool",
            "response": "Thank youu! <3"
        },
        {
            "author": "Cassie Storyweaver",
            "comment": "SO,.. the important question is: Belgian, or buttermilk? Also... is the phoenix reborn after you eat the waffles?",
            "response": "Always Belgian x3 (I'm biased, they're my neighbours so I only get to eat those xD)\r\nAnd nope, WafflePhoenixes that have turned into waffles do not reincarnate. Such is the tragedy of a \"failed\" experiment.. But they're widely available and new ones are made every day, so there's plenty to keep up with demand. ^^"
        },
        {
            "author": "DesdemonaRose",
            "comment": "Nice! This could turn into a new sort of DoorDash service too, especially if they could do more than waffles. Get hungry, your food just flies to you.",
            "response": "Never thought of using them that way!"
        }
    ],
